###  http://edugraph.io/edu/FractionSimplification
:FractionSimplification rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                                 edu:Area ;
                        edu:expands :Division ,
                                    :RatioEquivalence ;
                        edu:partOf :FractionNumbers ;
                        rdfs:isDefinedBy """Reducing a fraction to its simplest form by dividing the numerator and denominator by their greatest common factor.

Example: 12/18 simplifies to 2/3 by dividing both by 6""" .


